{"tid":2291682,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[試食有圖] 雞煲辣魚黃店 (內無精液太陽蛋)","createTime":"2020-11-19T03:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T03:27:30.000Z","uid":182895,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fe27a76fd916a06adf186799cd69379e03a8c187","tid":2291682,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"(好啦我唔再講大渣哥隻神級透明精液太陽蛋了)<br />\n <br />\n呢排試黃店中菜, 係Wolipay 見到呢間所以又去試下<br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">聚味軒</span></span><br />\n九龍城獅子石道40號地舖<br />\n <br />\n<span class=\"red\">Summary:</span><br />\n1) 內外無高調黃, 聽聞早期有係鋪頭派文宣<br />\n2) 電視係ViuTV<br />\n3) 環境整潔舒適, 服務好<br />\n4) 食物整體唔錯, 價錢合理, 可再J<br />\n <br />\n圖<br />\n<br />\n醉豬手<br />\n個汁唔錯, 唔算超入味, 還好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJOdYkZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJOdYkZ.png&h=5aa43ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蜜糖雞翼<br />\n香口但雞翼唔入味, 有雪味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMSN2NJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMSN2NJ.png&h=06640ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咕嚕肉<br />\n外脆, 汁唔錯酸甜適中, 肉質juicy, Good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJrWbLK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJrWbLK.png&h=73f070e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃金茄子<br />\n份量超多, 邪惡, Good J<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YeNa0zr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYeNa0zr.png&h=19a191de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞煲<br />\n正常, 唔太油, 可以再多d 乾蔥配料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnAoBe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnAoBe6.png&h=a40c3aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n辣魚<br />\n湯底唔錯, 魚質可以, 辣味適中<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJOdYs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJOdYs4.png&h=88dd6821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羊腩煲<br />\n個汁好香濃如果冇咁鹹仲好, 配料好入味, 肉質好, 肥瘦適中<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDtNimh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDtNimh.jpg&h=ab809030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人頭價: $300-400 (狂食價)<br />\n份量多適合4-6位<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"79e9eaa93c08bb3a44207f4bbf5732db2a627ae1","tid":2291682,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae83d6b4ba5b7b91ca120e49bc0b7ae3b80af34","tid":2291682,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e9eaa93c08bb3a44207f4bbf5732db2a627ae1","tid":2291682,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"雞, 魚, 羊煲 yes少少偏貴<br />\n小菜還好都幾大份"},{"pid":"bf712a57574940d1a551acd0ad7e8c2619863b10","tid":2291682,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae83d6b4ba5b7b91ca120e49bc0b7ae3b80af34","tid":2291682,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e9eaa93c08bb3a44207f4bbf5732db2a627ae1","tid":2291682,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"雞, 魚, 羊煲 yes少少偏貴<br />\n小菜還好都幾大份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"都幾貴 個煲一個洗唔洗120"},{"pid":"555e8de9eadf96a2b4ed2a812770b0868c7b3c4f","tid":2291682,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf712a57574940d1a551acd0ad7e8c2619863b10","tid":2291682,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae83d6b4ba5b7b91ca120e49bc0b7ae3b80af34","tid":2291682,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79e9eaa93c08bb3a44207f4bbf5732db2a627ae1","tid":2291682,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c